reviewText: Extremely happy that I ordered this, arrived in record time
I love Betty White and this is early TV. So the pace now seems a little slow, maybe jokes a little corny, but still funny. She is a gem.
I love this series with Betty White.  She is so funny getting herself into all kinds of situations.  A good family series to watch with anyone.

just a plain funny show.
when you like the old tv shows as I love Lucy, you surely will like this show too.
